            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-red-100 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                <AlertCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" />
                When Higher Levels of Care Are Needed
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Online treatment may not be appropriate when:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <XCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700">You're at risk for severe withdrawal symptoms requiring medical supervision</span>
