                  <span class="text-neutral-700">You have severe or unstable mental health conditions</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <XCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700">You need 24/7 monitoring or structured environment</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
